adviseScripts.text: Commander! I heard something interesting.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Someone said that if you eat something bitter,
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: mugwort-flavored or garlic-flavored Splendamin, then you'll become an adult. Is that true?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Actually, it'll turn you into a human.
It's true.
A Nikke can become human again?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: There's no way that Splendamin has that kind of effect.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Commander, do not fall for ridiculous rumors, okay?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Just as I thought! The rumors are true!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Hehe! I'm going to buy a bunch and eat them all!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I talk with Soline about becoming an adult.
You know, at the Outpost...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: there's a... toy store.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: N-not that I'm really interested!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: But... have you been there before?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I have.
I haven't.
Y-you have? When?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: You should have taken me with you! You're so mean!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Yeah? Th-then... Do you want to go with me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'm not interested! But, I just thought that you might want to go there.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: So, will you go with me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Soline and I plan a visit to the toy store.
Brid is so mean to me these days.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Every time I say something, she just sighs...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: And then she tells me to go away, because I'm noisy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Do you think she is too mean to me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Yes.
No.
Right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'm so relieved that you think the same way as me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Just like I thought, I wasn't the one acting childish!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: N-no?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Then you're a big meanie, too!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I soothe Soline, who is offended.
I'm so tired of Diesel only giving me strawberry candy all the time.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I don't even like candy that much.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I've suffered through it because it's from Diesel... And I can't stand it anymore!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: But... I think she will be upset if I ask for a different flavor.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: What should I do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Buy Diesel a new flavor of candy.
Lie down in front of Diesel and throw a tantrum because you want a different flavor.
Buy her new candy?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Hmm... That's a good idea.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I can give Diesel a present
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: and be freed from the tyranny of strawberry at the same time!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Perfect! I'll get right on it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'm not a kid!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I don't throw tantrums!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I talk with Soline about strawberry candy.
Commander, tell me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Imagine two people. One is cute, and the other is mature.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Which one would you date?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: The cute one.
The mature one.
... Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: That's not what I expected.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Why can't you just like the mature one?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: After all, I'm not cute at all...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Really? You'd like the mature one?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Hehe.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Just as I thought.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Just you wait! I'll become mature in no time!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I listen to Soline's lecture on becoming mature.
These days, when Diesel and Brid see me,
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: they keep patting my head and saying I'm cute.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I think it's because they've never seen me at my best.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: They don't know how competent and charismatic I am!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: What do I have to do for them to stop seeing me as cute?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Say "stop seeing me as cute" with your charisma.
Chug a cup of bitter coffee in front of them.
How do I talk with charisma?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Also, I already tried that before.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: But it doesn't get through. Instead, they pat my head even more.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Chug a bitter cup of coffee?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Hmm... I guess if they see me drinking bitter coffee without flinching, then their impressions will be changed.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Okay, might as well give it a try! Since I'm an adult and all!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: That's good advice. Thanks!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I discuss how to not look cute with Soline.
A couple days ago, I went to the park.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Cafe Sweety saw me and asked if I was a lost child!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Then they called those kid cops A.C.P.U. and Diesel to take me home!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I told them I was a Nikke, but they completely ignored me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'm so angry. How should I take revenge on them?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Next time you see them, report that some scary big sisters are bothering you.
Next time you see them, report them as missing children as well.
Scary big sisters?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: No! I won't call them big sisters!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Anyway, no matter how bad they might be, I'll never report them.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I need another solution.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: You mean, and an eye for an eye, a tooth for a tooth?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Hmm, I like it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'm going to report them, too!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Then they will know how embarrassing it is!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I explore ways to take revenge on Cafe Sweety with Soline.
So annoying. So annoying!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Today I was working at the station, minding my own business...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Then someone came up to me and said, "Isn't it illegal for children to be working?" But, I'm an adult!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Argh. I'm so angry! It's so annoying!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: That person just hasn't seen your competence yet.
Do you want to take revenge on that person?
That must be it, right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Just wait. One day I will show everyone my competence!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: They'll say that there is no attendant like Soline!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: What do you mean revenge? Take revenge on a passenger?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'm just saying I'm annoyed, that's all! You're so dumb!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I soothe Soline, who is enraged.
Commander.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: N-never mind.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Are you bored or something?
Do you want some candy?
N-no!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: You think I poke you every time I'm bored?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I was just... curious if you wanted to eat something.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: How did you know?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Can you read minds or something?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: That's so fascinating!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I have a joyful counseling time after putting some candy in Soline's mouth.
I saw that Nikke Rumani on TV.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: She said you need to exercise with weights to have an adult body.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: So, I'm going to start lifting weights today!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Then I'll grow taller and look more like an adult!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Do you really believe that you will grow taller?
Good luck.
Yes! Of course!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Hmm, you don't seem to agree.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Hmph!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Well, whether or not you support me...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'm still going to do my best!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I make exercise plans with Soline in hopes of helping her grow.
I'm not sure why, but I've been craving some good food for a while now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Preferably something sweet.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: You're just going through a growth spurt.
Be careful or else you'll be putting on the pounds.
A growth spurt?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: No wonder my body feels different than it did a few days ago.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: So that's what it was!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: What? That can't be it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: My weight hasn't changed! Gosh, you're so annoying!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Soline and I talk about the different foods that we have a craving for.
If we reclaim the surface, do you think we could go on a trip?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Traveling on a train... something like that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Sure we can. Let's start planning our itinerary.
It may be a little soon to be thinking of that...
The first thing I want to do is ride the AZX through the snowy terrain!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: And I want to make a snowman as well! What about you, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: You could have at least humored me for a minute...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I hope it's not too far down the line.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Soline about the future.
I wanted to buy Brid a coffee so I went to the Cafe and asked for an americano.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: But the employee there said a kid shouldn't be drinking coffee!!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: How rude!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: We'll go to a different café next time.
Let's have Brid and Diesel come with us.
For sure, I'm never going there again!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: There are plenty of other cafes around here.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I feel a lot better after talking to you!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: What would that change?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: If anything, it'd just make us all look even younger.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I help Soline look for other cafes.
Commander, do you like tall girls?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Or do you prefer someone smaller... like me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Personally, I prefer shorter women.
I'd prefer if they were about my height.
Do you really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Then I don't have to try so hard to grow taller.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: In that case...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: how many more centimeters do I have to grow...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'm gonna start drinking more milk.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Soline about height.
I think I need to change my image.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: First up is how I dress. What kind of clothing should I wear?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Something that's all business.
Something more casual.
I like the sound of that!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: That would probably make me look more mature.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Not that I'm not already mature!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Hmm... I don't think that's much different from how I dress now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: What other styles could I try?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I look for suitable styles with Soline.
I heard that married couples on the surface used to go on trips together.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: A... honeymoon, was it? Have you heard about this before?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I came back from one before.
It'd be nice for you and I to go on a honeymoon.
Hmm?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: What do you mean?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Wait... were you married before?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Huh...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Wh-what? Are you confessing your feelings for me? This is all so sudden...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: You're just pulling my leg, aren't you? Argh, you're the worst!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I dodged a beating from Soline the entire time we were talking.
Diesel and Brid are my best friends. I feel so carefree around them.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Do you think they feel the same way about me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'm sure they do.
Why don't you ask them?
Yeah, exactly! I'm sure the feeling is mutual!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: It feels nice knowing that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: No way! That'd be so awkward!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Not a word of this to anyone!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I listen to Soline as she spoke highly of Diesel and Brid.
I was about to brush my teeth yesterday, when I noticed something...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Diesel swapped the regular toothpaste for strawberry-flavored! Can you believe that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Strawberry candy is one thing, but strawberry toothpaste? No thanks.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: It probably tastes nice and sweet.
Let's change it to another toothpaste.
Well... it did end up tasting really nice actually...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: It was like brushing your teeth with candy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I can't complain.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Hmmm. We don't have to go that far.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: And the taste actually wasn't half bad after all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I listen to Soline tell me more about the strawberry toothpaste incident.
Commander, have you ever been in love?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I was watching TV today, and there was a show about people trying to find love.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: So it made me curious.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Of course, she's standing right in front of me.
Do you want to hear my love story?
Hm? In front of Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: W-wait for a second... me?! You're in love with me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: You better not be kidding around this time!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: NO!!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I don't want to hear it. Don't say it. I don't need to hear this.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I shouldn't have said anything...
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Soline and I have a conversation about love.
It's such a pain cleaning the AZX. This isn't a one-woman job!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I'd like to see Brid and Diesel try and do this on their own. Then they'd see how hard it is.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Let's go on strike.
I'll help you with the cleaning.
I don't think that would change anything.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Not to mention that Diesel that Brid are even busier than I am.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Really? You better not change your mind!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I was planning on getting back to it in a moment.
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: Good thing I brought this up with you, Commander!
adviseScripts.speaker: Soline

adviseScripts.text: I cleaned the AZX with Soline.
